{
  "chapter": "073",
  "title": "白起王翦列传",
  "translations": {
    "1": {
      "title": "白起崛起战功赫",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">白起</span>是<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">郿</span>地人。他善于用兵，侍奉<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">秦昭王</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦昭王\">昭王（秦昭王）</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十三年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">白起</span>担任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">左庶长</span>，率兵<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span>打<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>国的<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">新城</span>。这一年，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏冉\">穰侯（魏冉）</span>出任<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国之相，推举<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">任鄙</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汉中守</span>。第<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">明年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">白起</span>升为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">左更</span>，在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">伊阙</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>打<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>两国，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">斩首</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二十四万</span>，又<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">虏</span>获敌将<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公孙喜</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">拔</span>取<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">五城</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：白起\">起（白起）</span>升任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">国尉</span>。他渡过黄河<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">夺取</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>国<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">安邑</span>以东地区，直到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">乾河</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">明年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">白起</span>升为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">大良造</span>。<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>打<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>国，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">拔</span>取之，前后共<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻取</span>大小城邑<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">六十一</span>座。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">明年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：白起\">起（白起）</span>与<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">客卿</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：司马错\">错（司马错）</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>打<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">垣城</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">拔</span>取之。再过<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">五年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">白起</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>打<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">拔</span>取<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">光狼城</span>。再过<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">七年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">白起</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>打<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">拔</span>取<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">鄢</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">邓</span>等<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">五城</span>。第<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">明年</span>，又<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>打<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">拔</span>取<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">郢</span>都，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">烧</span>毁<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">夷陵</span>，于是向东打到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">竟陵</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>王逃离<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">郢</span>都，向东<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">走</span>逃，迁都到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">陈</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国把<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">郢</span>地设置为<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">南郡</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">白起</span>被封为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：白起\">武安君（白起）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：白起\">武安君（白起）</span>借势<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">夺取</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>地，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">平定</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">巫</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">黔中郡</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦昭王\">昭王（秦昭王）</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">三十四年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">白起</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>打<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>国，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">拔</span>取<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">华阳</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">逐走</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">芒卯</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">俘虏</span>了三位<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span>系将领，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">斩首</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">十三万</span>。又与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>将<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">贾偃</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">作战</span>，把他的士卒<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二万人</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">沉</span>入河中。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦昭王\">昭王（秦昭王）</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">四十三年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">白起</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>打<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>国的<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">陉城</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">拔</span>取<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">五城</span>，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">斩首</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">五万</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">四十四年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">白起</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>打<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">南阳</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">太行</span>要道，<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">断绝</span>了此道。"
    },
    "2": {
      "title": "上党归赵引长平",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">四十五年</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>国的<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">野王</span>。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">野王</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">投降</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">上党</span>与韩都的通道被<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">切断</span>。上党太守<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">冯亭</span>和<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">百姓</span>商议说：\"通往<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">郑</span>都的道路已经<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">断绝</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>国肯定无法再管辖我们这些<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">百姓</span>了。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>兵一天天逼近，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>国无力抵御，不如把<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">上党</span>归附给<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国如果接受我们，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国一定发怒，必定会<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>打<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国遭到兵祸，必会亲近<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>国。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>联合为一，就可以抵挡<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国。\" 于是派人通报<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵孝成王\">孝成王（赵孝成王）</span>和<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵豹\">平阳君（赵豹）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵胜\">平原君（赵胜）</span>共同商议。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵豹\">平阳君（赵豹）</span>说：\"不如不接受。接受它，祸患会比所得大。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵胜\">平原君（赵胜）</span>说：\"无缘无故得到一个郡，接受它更为有利。\" <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国就接受了上党，便<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">冯亭</span>为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：冯亭\">华阳君（冯亭）</span>。"
    },
    "3": {
      "title": "秦攻韩缑氏蔺",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">四十六年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>打<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>国的<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">缑氏</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">蔺</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">拔</span>取了它们。"
    },
    "4": {
      "title": "长平之战坑赵卒",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">四十七年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国派<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">左庶长</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王龁</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>打<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>国，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">夺取</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">上党</span>。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">上党</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">百姓</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">逃</span>往<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国驻军<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长平</span>，以接应<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">上党</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">百姓</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">四月</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：王龁\">龁（王龁）</span>于是<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>打<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">廉颇</span>为主将。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>军<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>卒冲撞<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>军侦察兵，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>军侦察兵<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">斩</span>杀了<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">裨将</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵茄\">茄（赵茄）</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">六月</span>，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">攻陷<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>军，攻取二处堡障和四个都尉。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">七月</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>军修筑壁垒坚守。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>军又<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>其壁垒，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">夺取</span>二尉，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻破</span>其阵形，〖[夺下其西面壁垒。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">廉颇</span>坚守壁垒以待<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>军，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>军多次挑<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">战</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>兵不出。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>王多次派人责备廉颇。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国丞相<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">应侯</span>又派人携带<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">千金</span>到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国施行反间计，声称：\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国所害怕的，只是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵括\">马服子（赵括）</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵括</span>为将而已。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">廉颇</span>很好对付，而且快要<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">投降</span>了。\" <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>王本来已对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">廉颇</span>军队屡次损兵、屡次<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">败</span>阵且又坚守不敢<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">战</span>感到恼怒，又听信了<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国反间之言，于是派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵括</span>取代<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">廉颇</span>为将，率兵<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span>攻<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国听说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵括\">马服子（赵括）</span>为将，便暗中派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：白起\">武安君（白起）</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">白起</span>担任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">上将军</span>，让<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王龁</span>改任尉职<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">裨将</span>，并在军中下令：有人胆敢泄露<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：白起\">武安君（白起）</span>为主将者<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">斩</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵括</span>到任后，就发兵<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>击<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>军。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>军假装<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">败</span>退<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">逃走</span>，而设置两支奇兵来<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">劫袭</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>军。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>军乘胜追击，直追到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>军壁垒。壁垒坚固无法攻入，而<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>军奇兵<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二万五千人</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">切断</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>军后路，又一支〖$五千骑</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">切断</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>军壁垒之间的联络，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>军被分为二段，粮道<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">断绝</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>军派出轻兵<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span>之。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>军作<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">战</span>不利，于是筑壁坚守，等待救兵。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>王听说<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国粮道已被<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">断绝</span>，亲自到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">河内</span>，赐<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">百姓</span>爵位各一级，征发十五岁以上所有男丁都赶赴<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长平</span>，拦截<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">断绝</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国的援军和粮食。"
    },
    "5": {
      "title": "白起坑杀赵降卒",
      "text": "到<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">九月</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国士卒已有<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">四十六日（时长）</span>没有粮食，暗中互相<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">残杀</span>而食。前来<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>军壁垒，想要突围。分成四队，轮番四五次攻击都无法突围。其将军<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵括</span>率领精锐士卒亲自搏<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">战</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>军<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">射</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵括</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵括\">括（赵括）</span>军溃<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">败</span>，士卒<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">四十万人</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">投降</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：白起\">武安君（白起）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：白起\">武安君（白起）</span>盘算道：\"先前<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国已经<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">拔</span>取了<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">上党</span>，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">上党</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">百姓</span>不愿为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国所有而归顺<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国士卒反复无常，如果不全部<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>掉，恐怕日后作乱。\" 于是用欺诈手段把他们全部<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">坑</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>，只留下其中年幼者<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二百四十人</span>放回<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国。前后<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">斩首</span>和<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">俘虏</span>共<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">四十五万人</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国举国震惊。"
    },
    "6": {
      "title": "应侯设隙止攻赵",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">四十八年</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十月</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国又重新<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">平定</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">上党</span>郡。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国把军队分为二路：<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王龁</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>打<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">皮牢</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">拔</span>取之；<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">司马</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：司马梗\">梗（司马梗）</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">平定</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">太原</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>两国恐惧，派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">苏代</span>用丰厚的礼物游说<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国丞相<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">应侯</span>说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：白起\">武安君（白起）</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">擒</span>获<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵括\">马服子（赵括）</span>了吗？\" 答：\"是。\" 又问：\"那要<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">围</span>攻<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">邯郸</span>了吗？\" 答：\"是。\" \"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国一亡则<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>王便成帝王，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：白起\">武安君（白起）</span>就会位列<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">三公</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：白起\">武安君（白起）</span>为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">战</span>胜<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">取</span>的城邑有<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">七十余城</span>，南面<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">平定</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">鄢</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">郢</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">汉中</span>，北面<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">擒</span>获<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵括</span>之军，即便是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>公旦、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：召公奭\">召（召公奭）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕望</span>的功劳也不会超过这些。如今<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国灭亡，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>王称帝，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：白起\">武安君（白起）</span>必位列<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">三公</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">您</span>能甘居其下吗？即便不想居其下，也不得不如此。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国曾经<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>打<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>国，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">围</span>攻<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">邢丘</span>，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">围困<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">上党</span>，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">上党</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">百姓</span>都<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">反</span>投<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国，<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>不愿做<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">百姓</span>已经<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">很久（时长）</span>了。如今灭掉<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">北地</span>归入<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>国，东面之地归入<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国，南面之地归入<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>，那您所能得到的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">百姓</span>也没多少人。不如借此机会让韩赵割地求和，不要把这件功劳记在<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：白起\">武安君（白起）</span>身上。\" 于是<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">应侯</span>向<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>王进言：\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>兵疲劳，请允许<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>割地求和，暂且让<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>卒休整。\" 秦王听从了，割<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">垣雍</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>〖$六城</span>以讲和。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">正月</span>，双方都罢兵。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：白起\">武安君（白起）</span>听说这事，从此与<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">应侯</span>有了嫌隙。"
    },
    "7": {
      "title": "强征不从赐死杜邮",
      "text": "那一年<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">九月</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国又出兵，派五<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大夫</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王陵</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>打<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">邯郸</span>。当时<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：白起\">武安君（白起）</span>正患病，不能出征。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">四十九年</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">正月</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：王陵\">陵（王陵）</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>打<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">邯郸</span>，收获不大，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国增派兵力辅助<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：王陵\">陵（王陵）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：王陵\">陵（王陵）</span>军队损失了五校。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：白起\">武安君（白起）</span>病愈，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>王想让<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：白起\">武安君（白起）</span>取代<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：王陵\">陵（王陵）</span>为将。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：白起\">武安君（白起）</span>进言说：\"<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">邯郸</span>实在不好<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>打。况且<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>救兵每天都在赶来，那些<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>怨恨<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国已<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">很久（时长）</span>了。现在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>虽然<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻破</span>了<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长平</span>军，但<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>军死者过半，国内空虚。远渡<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">河山</span>去争夺别人的国都，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国在内里响应，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>从外面<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>击，必然会<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻破</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>军。此事不可行。\" <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>王亲自下令，白起不去；又派<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">应侯</span>请求，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：白起\">武安君（白起）</span>始终推辞不肯前往，于是称病。"
    },
    "8": {
      "title": "白起赐死杜邮",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>王派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王龁</span>取代<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：王陵\">陵（王陵）</span>为将，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">围</span>攻<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">邯郸</span>八、<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">九月</span>，未能<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻拔</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黄歇\">春申君（黄歇）</span>和<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：信陵君\">魏公子（信陵君）</span>率<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数十万</span>兵<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>击<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>军，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>军损失很多。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：白起\">武安君（白起）</span>说：\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国不听我的计策，如今怎样了！\" <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>王听到此话，发怒，强逼<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：白起\">武安君（白起）</span>出山，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：白起\">武安君（白起）</span>便称病重。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">应侯</span>请求，也不起身。于是<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">免</span>去<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：白起\">武安君（白起）</span>爵位，贬为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>卒，流放到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">阴密</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：白起\">武安君（白起）</span>抱病未能动身。过了<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">三月</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>击<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>军猛烈，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>军屡次败退，使者每天报告。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>王便派人打发<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">白起</span>，不许他留在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">咸阳</span>城内。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：白起\">武安君（白起）</span>出发后，出<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">咸阳</span>西门<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">十里</span>，到达<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">杜邮</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">秦昭王</span>与<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">应侯</span>、<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">群臣</span>商议说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">白起</span>被流放时，仍然闷闷不服，颇有怨言。\" <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>王于是派使者赐他<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">剑</span>，让他自<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">裁。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：白起\">武安君（白起）</span>拿起<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">剑</span>将要自〖[刎时说：\"我对上天有什么罪过而至于此呢？\" 过了许久，又说：\"我本来就〖[当死。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长平</span>之<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">战</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国士卒<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">投降</span>的有〖$数十万人</span>，我用欺诈手段把他们全部<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">坑</span>杀，这足以死罪。\" 于是<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">自杀</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：白起\">武安君（白起）</span>的死，发生在<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">秦昭王</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">五十年</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十一月</span>。死而非其罪，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国人同情他，乡里都为他立祠<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">祭祀</span>。"
    },
    "9": {
      "title": "王翦破赵灭燕魏",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王翦</span>是<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">频阳</span>东乡人。少年时就喜好兵法，侍奉<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">秦始皇</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦始皇\">始皇（秦始皇）</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十一年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：王翦\">翦（王翦）</span>率兵<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>打<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">阏与</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻破</span>之，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">拔</span>取<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">九城</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十八年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：王翦\">翦（王翦）</span>率兵<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>打<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国。过了<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">一年多</span>，终于<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻拔</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>王<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">投降</span>，全部<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">平定</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>地设为郡。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">明年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">荆轲</span>到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国行刺，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>王派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王翦</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>打<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>国。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：姬喜\">王喜（姬喜）</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">逃</span>往<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">辽东</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：王翦\">翦（王翦）</span>于是<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">平定</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>都<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">蓟</span>而返。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：王翦\">翦（王翦）</span>之<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王贲</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国·规范：楚\">荆（楚）</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国·规范：楚\">荆（楚）</span>兵大<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">败</span>。然后回师<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>国，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>王<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">投降</span>，于是<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">平定</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>地。"
    },
    "10": {
      "title": "李信惨败王翦出山",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">秦始皇</span>已<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span>掉三<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">逐走</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>王，又屡次<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻破</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国·规范：楚\">荆（楚）</span>师。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>将<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李信</span>年少壮勇，曾经率<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数千</span>兵<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">追逐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：燕太子丹\">丹（燕太子丹）</span>到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">衍水</span>中，终于<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻破</span>并擒获<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：燕太子丹\">丹（燕太子丹）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦始皇\">始皇（秦始皇）</span>认为他贤能勇猛。于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦始皇\">始皇（秦始皇）</span>问<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李信</span>：\"我想<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">取</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国·规范：楚\">荆（楚）</span>国，依<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span>估计，用多少人足够？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李信</span>回答：\"不过用<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二十万人</span>。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦始皇\">始皇（秦始皇）</span>问<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王翦</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王翦</span>说：\"非<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">六十万人</span>不可。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦始皇\">始皇（秦始皇）</span>说：\"王<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span>老了，怎么这样胆怯！李<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span>果然气势雄壮勇武，他说得对。\" 于是派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李信</span>和<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蒙恬</span>率<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二十万</span>军南下<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国·规范：楚\">荆（楚）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王翦</span>之言未被采纳，因此称病，告老返回<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">频阳</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李信</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>打<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">平与</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蒙恬</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>打<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名·规范：寝邑\">寝（寝邑）</span>，大<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国·规范：楚\">荆（楚）</span>军。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李信\">信（李信）</span>又<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>打<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">鄢</span>郢，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻破</span>之，于是引兵向西，与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蒙恬</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">城父</span>会合。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国·规范：楚\">荆（楚）</span>人随后追赶，<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">三日（时长）</span>三夜不停歇，大<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李信</span>军，攻入两座壁垒，<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>死七名<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">都尉</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>军败<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">逃</span>。"
    },
    "11": {
      "title": "请田自坚伐楚成功",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦始皇\">始皇（秦始皇）</span>听说此事，大怒，亲自驾车前往<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">频阳</span>，向<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王翦</span>谢罪道：\"我因没有采用<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span>之计，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李信</span>果然让<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>军受<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">辱。现在听说<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国·规范：楚\">荆（楚）</span>兵日益向西进逼，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span>虽然患病，怎忍心抛弃我呢！\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王翦</span>推辞说：\"老<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>病弱昏乱，恳请大王另择贤将。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦始皇\">始皇（秦始皇）</span>再次道歉：\"算了，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span>不要再说了！\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王翦</span>说：\"大王如果一定要任用<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>，非<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">六十万人</span>不可。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦始皇\">始皇（秦始皇）</span>说：\"全听<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span>安排。\" 于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王翦</span>率〖$六十万人</span>大军，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦始皇\">始皇（秦始皇）</span>亲自送至<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">灞上</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王翦</span>出发时，请求赏赐许多美田宅园池。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦始皇\">始皇（秦始皇）</span>说：\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span>此去即可，何愁贫穷呢？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王翦</span>说：\"为大王做将军，有功终究不能<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span>侯，所以趁大王顾念<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>的时候，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>也及时请求园池作为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子孙</span>的产业罢了。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦始皇\">始皇（秦始皇）</span>大笑。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王翦</span>已到函谷关，又派使者五批回去请求赐赏良田。有人说：\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span>乞求赏赐，也太过分了。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王翦</span>说：\"不是这样。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>王粗暴而不信任人。如今把<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦国</span>全部<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">甲士</span>都委托给我一人，我不多请求田宅为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子孙</span>作产业来自证心迹，倒要让<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>王平白地怀疑我吗？\""
    },
    "12": {
      "title": "王翦代李信破楚",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王翦</span>果然取代<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李信</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国·规范：楚\">荆（楚）</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国·规范：楚\">荆（楚）</span>听说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王翦</span>增兵而来，就把全国的兵力都调来〖[抵抗<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王翦</span>到达后，坚守营垒不出战，不肯<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">作战</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国·规范：楚\">荆（楚）</span>兵数次挑<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">战</span>，秦军始终不出。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王翦</span>每天让<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>卒休整洗浴，供给好饮食以抚慰，亲自与<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>卒同食。过了很久，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王翦</span>派人问军中在做什么游戏？回答说：\"正在投石、跳远。\" 于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王翦</span>说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>卒可以使用了。\" <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国·规范：楚\">荆（楚）</span>军数次挑<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">战</span>而<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>军不出，于是引兵东撤。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：王翦\">翦（王翦）</span>便发兵<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">追击</span>，命壮<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>出<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span>，大<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国·规范：楚\">荆（楚）</span>军。在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">蕲南</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>掉其<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项燕</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国·规范：楚\">荆（楚）</span>兵于是溃<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">败</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">逃</span>散。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>乘胜进而略<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">定</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国·规范：楚\">荆（楚）</span>地的各城邑。过了<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">一年多</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">俘</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：楚王\">荆王（楚王）</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">负刍</span>，终于〖[平定<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国·规范：楚\">荆（楚）</span>地，改为郡县。又向南〖[征百<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>之<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>。而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王翦</span>之<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王贲</span>与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李信</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻破</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">平定</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>地。"
    },
    "13": {
      "title": "平天下王蒙建功",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">秦始皇</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二十六年</span>，全部[兼并了<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>，<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">王氏</span>、<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">蒙氏</span>的功劳最多，名声流传后世。"
    },
    "14": {
      "title": "王离被虏降诸侯",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦二世\">二世（秦二世）</span>之时，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王翦</span>和他的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：王贲\">贲（王贲）</span>都已经去世，而<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">蒙氏</span>又被<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span>族。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈胜</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">反</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王翦</span>之<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">孙</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王离</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">围</span>攻<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>王及<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张耳</span>于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">钜鹿</span>城。有人说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王离</span>是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国的名将。如今统领强<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>之兵，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>打新立的<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国，攻克是必然的。\" 有客说：\"不然。为将三代以上必<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">败</span>。为什么必<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">败</span>呢？因为他们所<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span>的人太多，后人就会承受那不祥之报。现在<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王离</span>已经<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">三世（时长）</span>为将了。\" 没过多久，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项羽</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">救</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span>败<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>军，果然<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">俘</span>获<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王离</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王离</span>军队于是<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">投降</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>。"
    },
    "15": {
      "title": "太史公曰",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太史公</span>说：俗话说\"尺有所短，寸有所长\"。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">白起</span>料敌制胜，变化无穷，声震<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>，但仍不能在<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">应侯</span>那里救自己于祸患。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王翦</span>身为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国大将，<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">削平</span><span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">六国</span>，在当时，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：王翦\">翦（王翦）</span>为老将，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦始皇\">始皇（秦始皇）</span>以他为师，但他不能辅佐<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国建立德政、巩固根本，而是苟且迎合、取悦上意，以至于寿终。到他的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">孙</span>子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王离</span>被<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项羽</span>所<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">俘</span>获，不也是理所当然的吗！他们各自都有短处。"
    },
    "16": {
      "title": "赞",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">白起</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王翦</span>，都善于用兵。 先后为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国大将，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">拔</span>取<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻破</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国·规范：楚\">荆（楚）</span>。 <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国任用<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵奢\">马服（赵奢）</span>，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长平</span>于是被<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">坑</span>杀。 <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国〖[陷害<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李信</span>，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">霸上</span>出兵远征。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：王贲\">贲（王贲）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：王离\">离（王离）</span>相继出仕，<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">三代</span>再无英名。"
    }
  }
}